{"tid":363037,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"(npsleep)500蚊故解析","createTime":"2017-08-17T10:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T17:47:12.000Z","uid":55369,"like":78,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e14a8b3b6fdf3b7f8ea3c159c3f3276740f651c","tid":363037,"uid":55369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:55:49.000Z","msg":"如題，其實想創造返個有本土味既nosleep 故，亦都係一個拋磚黎，打算之後開返個nosleep 集中post 。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解會有個咁既故係到</span><br />\n<br />\n係真係有個朋友同我講有人比左封利是佢（冇收）<br />\n<br />\n之後既一段笑話而引出黎既諗頭<br />\n<br />\n如果跟我個劇本行既話其實係個3日長既故<br />\n<br />\n個故事大概得5%係真<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">做咩斷得咁突然</span><br />\n<br />\n其實話就話3日既故，但本身已經設計好左2個收尾位。而我選擇左呢一個。<br />\n<br />\nnosleep 故既其中一個規則係無論有幾過火，不可思異，讀者可以唔信或者去<span style=\"color: red;\">質疑</span> ，但你唔好去破壞 e.g <span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再流D or 起底啦假膠黎</span> 。<br />\n<br />\nstorytelling 我本身個感受其實都重要，我要相信我真係&quot;呃到&quot;你地，你地真係&quot;相信&quot; 。<br />\n<br />\n但有人起底同不停打擊我唔係咁舒服，而我只係第一次寫故，有興趣既巴絲有機會再比個體驗你。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個故其實仲有少少伏筆，關於個故可以問下問題睇下解唔解答到唔明既地方</span>"},{"pid":"17eb2676730aacebc26601c9579dd88aca2fc39e","tid":363037,"uid":55369,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">R</span>%&amp;%&amp;*<span style=\"color: red;\">e</span>%<span style=\"color: red;\">x</span>&amp;**%*<span style=\"color: red;\">j</span>&amp;<span style=\"color: red;\">&upsilon;</span>%<span style=\"color: red;\">st</span><code>%&trade;⌘*&beta;&pi;%*[]</code>_%<span style=\"color: red;\">g</span>%%&amp;<span style=\"color: red;\">o</span>`&amp;*<span style=\"color: red;\">n</span>&beta;&infin;<span style=\"color: red;\">e</span>&upsilon;</blockquote>"},{"pid":"94aeb6860ed4317cc289d6c5bceb8a3926221749","tid":363037,"uid":90820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"好好玩<br />\n都做到個氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ho